Package: xcircuit
Version: 2.3.3
Revision: 3
Maintainer: Max Horn <max@quendi.de>
Depends: x11, ghostscript, python (>= 2.2.1-8)
BuildDepends: m4, automake1.5, db3 (>= 3.3.11-11), readline (>= 4.3-5), gdbm, gmp, expat, tcltk-dev, dlcompat-dev
Source: http://xcircuit.ece.jhu.edu/archive/xcircuit-%v.tar.bz2
ConfigureParams: --mandir=%p/share/man
SetCPPFLAGS: -D__DARWIN__
CompileScript: <<
(%p/bin/aclocal-1.5;%p/bin/automake-1.5 --foreign; /usr/bin/autoconf;./configure %c;make)
<<
InstallScript: make install DESTDIR=%d
DocFiles: COPYRIGHT README*
Description: Circuit drawing app with schematic capture
DescUsage: <<
In some cases XCircuit uses cursors which are bigger than 16x16. In the
current version of XFree86, this does not work in rootless mode. Hence
you might want to switch to fullscreen mode when using xcircuit.
<<
